graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        HTTPRouteMgr[HTTPRoute Manager]
        RefGrantMgr[ReferenceGrant Manager]
        NetPolMgr[NetworkPolicy Manager]
        RBACMgr[RBAC Manager]
        ProxyConfigGen[kube-rbac-proxy Config Generator]
        DSPAIntegration[DSPA Integration]

        Controller -->|manages| HTTPRouteMgr
        Controller -->|manages| RefGrantMgr
        Controller -->|manages| NetPolMgr
        Controller -->|manages| RBACMgr
        Controller -->|manages| ProxyConfigGen
        Controller -->|manages| DSPAIntegration
        Webhook -->|injects sidecar| ProxyConfigGen
    end

    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| HTTPRoute[HTTPRoute<br/>Gateway API]
    Controller -->|creates| ReferenceGrant[ReferenceGrant<br/>Cross-namespace]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
    Controller -->|creates| RoleBinding[RoleBinding]
    Controller -->|creates| Secret[Pipeline Secret]

    Webhook -->|mutates| NotebookCR
    Webhook -->|injects| RBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Sidecar]

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Gateway[Gateway API<br/>v1.2.1]
        KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller]
        ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    end

    subgraph "Internal ODH Dependencies"
        DSGateway[Data Science Gateway<br/>openshift-ingress]
        DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>DSPA]
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle]
    end

    Controller -->|depends on| Gateway
    Controller -->|depends on| KubeflowController
    Controller -->|depends on| ServiceCA
    Controller -->|API calls| K8sAPI

    HTTPRoute -->|routes to| DSGateway
    DSPAIntegration -->|watches| DSPipelines
    Dashboard -->|creates| NotebookCR
    Controller -->|mounts| TrustedCA

    RBACProxy -->|authenticates| K8sAPI

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Gateway fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style DSGateway fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style DSPipelines fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style TrustedCA fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
